channel.title: [508] Insanity [508]
channel.description:
[center]
Since Legend's Ville is [b]DEAD[/b] I will replace the thread with this.
Insanity 508 will be based off of Berky-Scape, it has that nice, RuneScape like feeling, and the combat comes close to perfect.
[b]Minigames[/b] Pest Control: 99% Barrows: 99% Dueling: 50% Barbarian Assualt: 99% (95% credits to Davidi2, I fixed some glitches) Castle Wars: 99% (About 70% credits to Bulby, but I fixed many glitches) Fist of Guthix: Unstarted (Creds to that guy who gave me map data for the map data) Fight Pits: 99% (100% credits to TokkulScape)
[b]Skills[/b] Combat: 90% (Near perfect, credits to whoever made the combat) Range: 90% (Near perfect, credits to whoever made it) Mage: 85% (Near perfect, 5% credits to me for making delays on projectiles) Woodcutting: 90% (Near perfect, I fixed many glitches and added ents + nests) Mining: 99% (My favorite skill, near perfect, fixed many glitches + added breaks) Fishing: 70% (It's ok, barely did anything to it) Cooking: 90% (Near perfect, I added level requirements, and burning) Firemaking: 70% (Near perfect, except walk west is NOT clipped) Hunting: 10% (I didn't modify it, just clicking on birds and does animation and adds item) Construction: 10% (I didn't modify it, just commands to make new rooms) Summoning: 50% (You can summon, but no shards ect, I modified it so that summon npcs attack and you can attack them) Smithing: 50% (IDK)
Finishing the rest tommarow...
